### Software build outputs (sw/)
# The small compiled-C test images (sw/build/*.hex) ARE committed: they are the inputs to
# ProgramSpec, and CI has no RISC-V cross-compiler, so it could never regenerate them.
# Everything else under sw/build is intermediate and regenerable.
# NOTE: this must be path-specific rather than a bare `build/` -- git cannot re-include a file
# whose parent directory is excluded.
sw/build/*.elf
sw/build/*.bin
sw/build/*.dis
sw/build/*.map

# The ISA suite is large (48 images) and needs a 7 MB riscv-tests checkout, so it is generated
# on demand by sw/isa/build_isa.sh. IsaSpec skips cleanly when these are absent.
sw/isa/build/
sw/riscv-tests/

